article_text:
Sioux Falls, SD

Many people in Sioux Falls felt the luck of the Irish Saturday as they headed downtown to watch the 36th Annual St. Patrick's Day Parade.

We asked for photos of your time at the parade, and we're seeing a lot of green!

You can send us your photos by uploading them to uShare, or email them to at ushare@keloland.com.
